title: Burgerei
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Western, Fast food, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. For a lack of pure veg food in this town, this small burger shop next to the nightlife street of Kiel offers a veggie burger with seitan - vegans should specify.
